short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple tool used to modify HTTP requests and responses.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SetHead is a powerful Chrome application created for developers, testers, and tech enthusiasts who need to manipulate HTTP requests and responses effortlessly. With SetHead, you can customize headers, modify request payloads (coming soon!), and tweak response data (coming soon!) on the fly. Whether you're debugging, testing APIs, or experimenting with web development, SetHead offers a user-friendly interface to streamline your workflow and enhance your productivity.
